KaziWhmcs - Changelog
=====================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Updated: License headers

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Only usernames which belong to products set through the imscp module must be overridden using domain name

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: Filemanager and PhpMyAdmin buttons in client area
    Added: Option allowing to enable/disable sending of the i-MSCP welcome message
    Fixed: i-MSCP login button in client area doesn't work
    Fixed: Plugin doesn't work with non-standard ports
    Fixed: The generate_user_traffic() function has been renamed to shared_getCustomerStats() in latest i-MSCP code
    Fixed: Wrong (truncated) username in pending orders

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Configuration variable `WEB_FOLDER_PROTECTION` is missing

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: ChangePassword module command doesn't work
    Fixed: Do not force strong password - Lets WHMCS manage this

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Unset identity data on shutdown

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Implemented: ChangePassword module command
    Implemented: UsageUpdate module command

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    First release
